Metadata.Title: The Town Hall Final Boss
Metadata.Description: Welcome to Sapienza, Landslide.Targets: Bohemian, Salvatore Bravuomo, Photographer, Luigi (Green Plumber), Mario (Red Plumber).Required items for specific eliminations are obtained inside the Town Hall. Each target must be eliminated using their assigned Town Hall item while wearing the correct disguise.Kill only the targets, hide all the bodies and do not get recorded by a security camera during the mission.Complete the mission before 16:16.Only one exit available.Good luck.
